00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,360
How did Fatty

305
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:51,890
hurt his hand?

306
00:16:58,180 --> 00:16:59,060
Yesterday,

307
00:16:59,730 --> 00:17:02,460
he took the first place in the first three rounds.

308
00:17:02,940 --> 00:17:04,400
He was in a very good state.

309
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:05,780
I thought

310
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:07,490
Fatty would get the first medal

311
00:17:07,490 --> 00:17:08,700
