322
00:17:38,050 --> 00:17:39,210
But

323
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:41,960
I didn't see his face clearly.

324
00:17:44,950 --> 00:17:46,540
I only remember

325
00:17:46,570 --> 00:17:50,030
there were many people in the registration office yesterday.

326
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:52,690
Later,

327
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:55,570
I found that my shoelaces were loose.

328
00:18:45,570 --> 00:18:48,380
Can you recognize the person who stepped on you if you see him again?

329
00:18:48,380 --> 00:18:49,420
I think so.

330
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:51,060
He has curly hair.

331
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:54,840
The spikes... are blue.

332
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:58,120
He hurt someone severely,

333
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,980
but he didn't even apologize.

334
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,530
Do you think

335
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,770
someone did it on purpose?

336
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:07,250
I don't think it's very likely.

337
00:19:08,610 --> 00:19:10,410
It was just a small competition.

338
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:12,400
Everyone treated it as training.

339
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:14,020
It's not necessary to do this

340
00:19:14,020 --> 00:19:16,010
to win the first place, right?

341
00:19:17,430 --> 00:19:18,830
What if...

342
00:19:18,930 --> 00:19:20,090
he did it to prevent Fatty

343
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:22,890
from participating in the autumn championships?

344
00:19:30,700 --> 00:19:35,540
-Go!
-Go!

345
00:19:35,540 --> 00:19:39,010
-Go!
-Go!

346
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:43,290
-Go!
-Go!

347
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:49,660
-Go!
-Go!

348
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:58,060
-Go!
-Go!

349
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:00,250
-Go!
-Go!

350
00:20:02,890 --> 00:20:04,570
So this is what a track and field competition is like?

351
00:20:04,570 --> 00:20:05,980
It's so exciting.

352
00:20:06,530 --> 00:20:09,180
-Hurry!
-Go!

353
00:20:10,110 --> 00:20:11,120
Run!

354
00:20:11,140 --> 00:20:12,180
It's Xue Yiran.

355
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,860
Why is Xue Yiran here?

356
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:14,940
To make them embarrassed by defeating them?

357
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,210
Looks like so.

358
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:18,420
Professional athletes can't participate in such competitions, right?

359
00:20:18,420 --> 00:20:19,370
That's right.

360
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:29,290
How does it feel to return to the track?

361
00:20:30,490 --> 00:20:31,350
I feel nothing.

362
00:20:44,430 --> 00:20:45,870
You have to work harder

363
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,080
to outshine me, a genius.

364
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:05,300
Qi Tian. Qi Tian?

365
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:08,240
Is it that hot?

366
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:09,850
Are you okay?

367
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:12,970
Cut the crap.

368
00:21:14,930 --> 00:21:16,460
I have excessive internal heat. Is there a problem?

369
00:21:16,460 --> 00:21:17,460
Just look for him.

370
00:21:20,540 --> 00:21:22,700
Okay.

371
00:21:25,190 --> 00:21:27,450
Is that area for the people from Huainan?

372
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:30,450
He surpassed him!

373
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:31,380
Come on!

374
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:37,090
