379
00:21:45,660 --> 00:21:46,570
Let's go.

380
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:49,040
You are so happy after hurting someone.

381
00:21:49,290 --> 00:21:50,140
Come on!

382
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:51,180
-Go!
-Go!

383
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:54,080
Come on!

384
00:21:59,950 --> 00:22:01,070
Who are you guys?

385
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:02,410
It's none of your business.

386
00:22:02,410 --> 00:22:04,270
We're here for the guy next to you.

387
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:07,580
Me?

388
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:10,430
Did you hurt my teammate yesterday?

389
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:12,850
Your teammate?

390
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:15,480
Well, who are you guys?

391
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:17,410
Why should I answer your question?

392
00:22:18,610 --> 00:22:21,110
I'm the chief coach of the Xinghe Track and Field Team.

393
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:22,640
My team member You Qian said

394
00:22:22,850 --> 00:22:25,530
