395
00:22:26,430 --> 00:22:28,090
at about 3:20 p.m. yesterday.

396
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:34,830
Oh no, Captain.

397
00:22:35,300 --> 00:22:37,330
I think I did step on something yesterday.

398
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:38,410
But I was in a hurry,

399
00:22:38,430 --> 00:22:40,030
so I went to He's place first.

400
00:22:40,910 --> 00:22:41,740
It's all your fault,

401
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:42,580
you jinx.

402
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,360
I think...

403
00:22:47,780 --> 00:22:49,550
I think it was me.

404
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:52,100
What's the big deal?

405
00:22:52,660 --> 00:22:53,970
It's just a finger.

406
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:57,150
We can pay the medical expenses.

407
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:59,040
What kind of attitude is this?

408
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:01,320
Fatty can afford the medical expenses himself.

409
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:03,090
He can't participate in any competition over the next three months.

410
00:23:03,090 --> 00:23:04,130
Do you know that?

411
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,060
He got very good grades this time,

412
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:09,770
so you don't want him

413
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:13,050
to participate in the autumn championships, right?

414
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:16,100
That's not true.

415
00:23:16,630 --> 00:23:18,840
Huainan's athletes who participated in this time's competition

416
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:20,300
