419
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:26,320
just because you won the first place in a friendly match?

420
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,120
Really?

421
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:30,260
I remember

422
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:32,750
you are the fastest runner in Huainan.

423
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:35,260
Why has Huainan changed its standards

424
00:23:35,260 --> 00:23:38,320
for first-tier and second-tier athletes these years?

425
00:23:39,130 --> 00:23:39,790
You...

426
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:41,600
You are Xue Yiran?

427
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:43,880
Xue Yiran?

428
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,350
Why is he here?

429
00:23:46,070 --> 00:23:47,990
Is he here for the first place?

430
00:23:48,430 --> 00:23:50,890
I'm here to lead the team. Is there a problem?

431
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,970
Except you,

432
00:23:53,990 --> 00:23:55,540
