436
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:02,840
You deserve it if you really were stepped on.

437
00:24:05,330 --> 00:24:06,130
Really?

438
00:24:07,020 --> 00:24:08,260
I think

439
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:10,030
you are the ignorant one.

440
00:24:10,780 --> 00:24:12,760
I don't need to compete with you myself.

441
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,360
The three of them from Xinghe

442
00:24:17,820 --> 00:24:21,020
