443
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:22,780
Xue Yiran,

444
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:25,620
you can't participate in the competition.

445
00:24:25,620 --> 00:24:26,750
Stop pretending.

446
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:30,470
You...

447
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,290
Listen,

448
00:24:34,730 --> 00:24:36,170
after the competition is over,

449
00:24:36,170 --> 00:24:37,620
